dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Outagamie_HydroLine_2016.gdb.[This is a line feature class identifying the location of all non-navigable and navigable water within Outagamie County. It is a county-wide file including all USGS designated navigable waterways and all non-navigable waterways.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
